Dear Eve,

Do you have Financial Management abilities, new projects in need of
funding or existing businesses requiring expansion?

We are investing a vast wealth on behalf of an angel Investor and
would be delighted to work with you.
Please you will be required to come down here immediately and see
things with your two eyes and feel it.
We are talking of investing US$500 million in your country.


The family owner representative of this fund is in Nairobi - Kenya, to
have meetings with you and to discuss terms and conditions.

Regards
Johan Boomsma
